                AND STR_TO_DATE(checkIn, '%d %M %Y') BETWEEN '2017-12-01' AND '2017-12-31'</pre><pre>SELECT *, a.id AS pid FROM wp_properties a

                WHERE b.gpxRegionID='1475'
                AND (WeekType='BonusWeek' OR WeekType='RentalWeek')
                AND STR_TO_DATE(checkIn, '%d %M %Y') BETWEEN '2018-01-01' AND '2018-01-31'</pre><pre>stdClass Object

                AND (WeekType='BonusWeek' OR WeekType='RentalWeek')
                AND STR_TO_DATE(checkIn, '%d %M %Y') BETWEEN '2017-09-01' AND '2017-09-30'</pre><pre>SELECT *, a.id AS pid FROM wp_properties a

                AND STR_TO_DATE(checkIn, '%d %M %Y') BETWEEN '2017-10-01' AND '2017-10-31'</pre><pre>UPDATE `wp_properties` SET `active` = 0 WHERE `id` = '5611'</pre><pre>UPDATE `wp_properties` SET `active` = 0 WHERE `id` = '5612'</pre><pre>UPDATE `wp_properties` SET `active` = 0 WHERE `id` = '5613'</pre><pre>UPDATE `wp_properties` SET `active` = 0 WHERE `id` = '5614'</pre><pre>UPDATE `wp_properties` SET `active` = 0 WHERE `id` = '7279'</pre><pre>UPDATE `wp_properties` SET `active` = 0 WHERE `id` = '7280'</pre><pre>stdClass Object
